snippet.title: Best VGM 1169 - Journey - Apotheosis
snippet.description:
OST available on iTunes : http://itunes.apple.com/us/album/journey-original-soundtrack/id511359368

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PS3
Journey (2012)
Apotheosis
Austin Wintory
